dc_title_s: Civitas Londinum.; Publisher's title: Plan of London (circa 1560-1570) by Ralph Agas
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Bird's-eye-view. Includes ill., text and coats-of-arms. 1 view on 8 sheets; 70 x 182 cm, sheets 59 x 44 cm and 44 x 59 cm This map is in the public domain.
